columns.name: species
columns.description: The species of penguins. Possible values are Adelie, Chinstrap, and Gentoo.

columns.name: island
columns.description: The island where the penguins were observed. Possible values are Torgersen, Biscoe, and Dream.

columns.name: bill_length_mm
columns.description: The length of the penguin's bill in millimeters. Ranges from 30.0 to 65.0 mm.

columns.name: bill_depth_mm
columns.description: The depth of the penguin's bill in millimeters. Ranges from 13.0 to 23.0 mm.

columns.name: flipper_length_mm
columns.description: The length of the penguin's flipper in millimeters. Ranges from 150.0 to 250.0 mm.

columns.name: body_mass_g
columns.description: The body mass of the penguin in grams. Ranges from 2000.0 to 7000.0 g.

columns.name: sex
columns.description: The sex of the penguin. Possible values are MALE and FEMALE. Missing values are marked as 'UNKNOWN'.

description.max_ids: An identifier for the data set version.
description.row_privacy: Indicates whether row-level privacy measures are applied.
description.censor_dims: Specifies whether dimensions are censored to protect privacy.

tableSchema.description: A dataset describing penguin species with measurements and metadata. Includes information on species, location, and physical attributes.
